<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1171.104142.figure20>
    dc:description "Figure 20. Aedeagi of the Novochares sallaei species group A-E N. chaquensis F N. garciai G-I N. dicranospathus J-L N. atratus M-R N. sallaei A-C Argentina D Costa Rica E Trinidad M-P Guatemala Q, R Mexico A, D-G, J, M, Q dorsal view B, H, K, N, R ventral view C, I, L, O lateral view P oblique view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/881187" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1171.104142.figure22>
    dc:description "Figure 22. Distribution of Novochares sallaei species group A N. cochlearis (red: circles, examined specimens; squares, literature / unconfirmed records), N. dicranospathus (yellow), N. pastinum (blue) B N. atratus (red: circles, examined specimens; squares, literature / unconfirmed records), N. clavieri (yellow), N. bisinuatus (blue), N. garciai (green) C N. chaquensis (red: circles, examined specimens; squares, literature / unconfirmed records), N. pichilingue (yellow) D N. fernandezae (red), N. tridentis (yellow), N. quadrispinus (blue), N. unguis (green)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/881189" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

